API Gateway
REST HTTPS - JSON API

- GET /tournaments
- POST /tournaments
- GET /tournaments/{tournamentId}

- POST /tournaments/{tournamentId}/subadmins
- POST /tournaments/{tournamentId}/notifications

- POST /tournaments/{tournamentId}/tickets
- GET /tickets/{ticketId}

Operaciones de Vistas:
- POST /tournaments/{tournamentId}/views
- GET /tournaments/{tournamentId}/views
- POST /views/{viewId}/join
Operaciones de Usuarios:
- POST /users
- GET /users/{userId}
